&lt;p&gt;Follow the execution of your page. Step through it line by line. When you are outputting the HTML shown above, you haven't got a value set for &lt;code&gt;field_myear&lt;/code&gt;. You need to be sure you are setting it prior to trying to output it - or you need to check your variable name to make certain that it is correct and doesn't have a typo in it.&lt;/p&gt;
