&lt;p&gt;I think that's will be helpful. Use &lt;code&gt;extract()&lt;/code&gt; in PHP. See example below&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;$array = (
         "bantya" =&amp;gt; "BANTYA",
         "sontya" =&amp;gt; "SONTYA",
         "niltya" =&amp;gt; "NILTYA" 
  );
  extract($array);
  var_dump($bantya);&lt;/code&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And you obtain new var: &lt;code&gt;$bantya&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;$sontya&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;$niltya&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
