&lt;p&gt;If you want to use some kind of globally available message bag. You can do the following in your Service Provider register method:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;$this-&amp;gt;app-&amp;gt;singleton('my.logging', function() {
