});
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Make sure your service provider is registered.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can now call this in your middleware using:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;$logBag = App::make('my.logging');
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See the &lt;a href="http://devdocs.io/laravel~5.1/api/5.1/illuminate/support/messagebag" rel="nofollow"&gt;API documentation&lt;/a&gt; on how to use the message bag.&lt;/p&gt;
