&lt;p&gt;To get current root, you can also use :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="http://php.net/manual/en/function.getcwd.php" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;getcwd()&lt;/a&gt; function.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;dirname(__FILE__)&lt;/code&gt;, you can get &lt;a href="http://php.net/manual/en/language.constants.predefined.php" rel="nofollow noreferrer"&gt;more here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
